pkgn:note_ID_1235546381 a pkg:PersonalNote ;
    dc:title """PITCH STRUCTURE:
    

      ￼
    

       Introduce yourself and your team name
    

      ￼
    

       What problem are you trying to solve
    

      ￼
    

       What is your idea or the solution you are working on
    

      ￼
    

        How does it work in practice (DEMO TIME)
    

      ￼
    

        Screencast of your demo, show us a flow of a user going through your application, and tell us what is happening on the screen or show your hardware product and explain how it works.
    

      ￼
    

        How do you build a business out of it? What is your business model?
    

      ￼
    

        What are your teams plans for the future?
    

      ￼
    

        Talk about your team and how committed you are to keep working on this
    

      ￼
    

       Strong closing statement!
    

      
    

      Your pitch should have around 200-240 words. Write it out and use word count to know its length!""" .

